{"tid":2411223,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網民假App、鬼機安心出逃  避留私隱洩行蹤 大狀：隨時犯法","createTime":"2021-02-17T07:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T08:07:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a84fe24670b7210f4485d3cf3dd2a8df31e9ae","tid":2411223,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:36:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/IXMIMWNTXJFRHAXCJYTIO6Y53A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FIXMIMWNTXJFRHAXCJYTIO6Y53A%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=53b3e166\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FIXMIMWNTXJFRHAXCJYTIO6Y53A%2F&h=3a9488ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/IXMIMWNTXJFRHAXCJYTIO6Y53A/</a><br />\n<br />\n網民假App、鬼機安心出逃 <br />\n避留私隱洩行蹤 大狀：隨時犯法<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府宣佈顧客初七起進入食肆及指定場所，需使用「安心出行」應用程式或登記個人資料，經營者違規將被罰停業。新措施被指疑收集市民行蹤，有專家指程式索取權限遠多於防疫用途，如何避開監察成為熱話，幾可亂真的仿製程式、手寫填報假資料等方法湧現，有大律師提醒做法或觸犯法律，但認為搜證或執法相當困難。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：隊目列超級傳播者 70消防送檢<br />\n<br />\n港府以防疫為由，去年推出「安心出行」應用程式監察市民行蹤。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n消息一出，坊間反對聲音紛起，皆。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：趕檢測復工 百人逼爆社區中心<br />\n<br />\n資訊科技界選委黃浩華表示，現時版本。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港人紛紛討論如何能避開監控。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有網民亦發現關閉手機網絡功能可如常使用「安心出行」，換言之，可準備一部無SIM卡的「鬼機」作為「安心出行」專用機。但黃提醒，要注意程式可被設定為隨時偵測網絡狀況，待有可用訊號後即發送資料，並非百分百安全。普遍意見亦認為此做法將增加安心出行下載量，等同為政府監控賦予認受性，主流聲音仍是杯葛使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3niSa48KdkJDPiowtvJ_jW0x2ac=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WAGKVR4NUZFEXOPZOW6B7RMNEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3niSa48KdkJDPiowtvJ_jW0x2ac%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWAGKVR4NUZFEXOPZOW6B7RMNEQ.jpg&h=addccb29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有餐廳為不欲使用「安心出行」的顧客放置資料卡收集箱，並承諾定期銷毀資料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n性質屬行騙 惟難執法<br />\n<br />\n有討論建議登記個人資料時填報假姓名及假電話號碼。執業大律師陸偉雄指，若有人因使用假應用程式或假資料而獲許可進入場地，性質等同行騙，有機會觸犯不誠實使用電腦或行使虛假文書罪行。但他認為若要執法，搜證有難度，「或者畀人delete咗，或者佢遺失咗，有好多原因」；疫情下人人戴口罩，就算有閉路電視片段亦難辨身份。<br />\n<br />\n政府資訊科技總監辦公。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BhMQGljvpX_S0FQnAreYOkBEeA8=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LXSLYPZOKZHILJT7KKRVF7WKLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBhMQGljvpX_S0FQnAreYOkBEeA8%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLXSLYPZOKZHILJT7KKRVF7WKLU.jpg&h=d22ed95f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有網民在討論區發表模仿「安心出行」的應用程式，介面與正版幾可亂真，可輸入任意地址。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eVAe1nLM3wZdLJkQPTkRnO6F8Rw=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OOLWQNON3BFO7BFNROYTNOJW4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeVAe1nLM3wZdLJkQPTkRnO6F8Rw%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOOLWQNON3BFO7BFNROYTNOJW4U.jpg&h=097c8f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■初七起顧客進入指定場所如健身中心等，須使用「安心出行」或登記個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/We6OyCgX0kWCaWOJV2mMiXYwMvM=/546x486/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OIEA6YACLZD3NGXTFGIQSNSOUU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWe6OyCgX0kWCaWOJV2mMiXYwMvM%3D%2F546x486%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOIEA6YACLZD3NGXTFGIQSNSOUU.gif&h=105dfbcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃浩華"},{"pid":"c4e5b0810cfea7582cfdbc7c38a9b7b694417e45","tid":2411223,"uid":79351,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:39:06.000Z","msg":"依家係你想呃鳩我在先，防止你呃鳩我又係我犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78454521dfab6e4dd4ee15d132216c15067052e","tid":2411223,"uid":45910,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c4e5b0810cfea7582cfdbc7c38a9b7b694417e45","tid":2411223,"uid":79351,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:39:06.000Z","msg":"依家係你想呃鳩我在先，防止你呃鳩我又係我犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:41:25.000Z","msg":"港共最撚難聽就係「依法」兩個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8869b5358ca8908da5fa975a0208c5242f769e","tid":2411223,"uid":144626,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:43:43.000Z","msg":"毒果你好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f893c7120149dd4442164d87f66fb883aef695fe","tid":2411223,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b8869b5358ca8908da5fa975a0208c5242f769e","tid":2411223,"uid":144626,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:43:43.000Z","msg":"毒果你好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:48:55.000Z","msg":"根本紅媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4510daff24ebc225df1a580f4c29019290b9e8f","tid":2411223,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:54:30.000Z","msg":"支持蘋果潑冷水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364be20119aac77968e07b3863ac54d88d81f013","tid":2411223,"u